      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with factory-spec individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This example boasts comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented subframe reinforcement, ACL rod bearing replacement, and a full VANOS overhaul. Power is delivered through a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by refreshed bushings and a factory-correct suspension geometry. Meticulously maintained with an unblemished interior and original paint depth, this vehicle offers the mechanical purity and high-revving performance the M-division is renowned for.",
