    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle is a fastidiously maintained example that has spent its life in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paintwork is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster free from swirl marks, stone chips, or any imperfections; it has been further protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating. All factory body panels are perfectly aligned, and the original alloy wheels are devoid of any curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history consisting exclusively of authorized dealership stamps. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, reflecting the mechanical integrity of a vehicle that has been cared for without regard to cost. This is an uncompromising specimen for the discerning enthusiast who seeks a 'like-new' experience.",
